	(1, 'Có rất nhiều nội dung thú vị trong những bài học tiếng anh', '2024-06-29 13:42:13.796484', 'https://study4.com/media/examprep/Post/files/2024/06/26/ielts_speaking_p2_sample_12.png', 'bài học tiếng anh giỏi'),
	(2, 'Để học tiếng Anh hiệu quả, bạn nên tạo môi trường thực hành bằng cách sử dụng tiếng Anh thường xuyên và tham gia các hoạt động như học lớp, xem phim hoặc đọc sách bằng tiếng Anh.', '2024-06-29 15:57:53.767189', 'https://study4.com/media/examprep/Post/files/2024/06/26/ielts_speaking_p2_sample_12.png', 'Làm sao để học tiếng anh hiệu quả?'),
	(3, 'Last summer, I embarked on an unforgettable journey by public transport to explore the vibrant city of Barcelona with a group of close friends. We hopped on a double-decker bus, eager to soak in the sights and sounds of this bustling metropolis. As we navigated through the city streets, we marveled at the stunning architecture, bustling markets, and colorful street art that adorned every corner.\r\n\r\nWe visited iconic landmarks like the Sagrada Familia and Park Güell, immersing ourselves in the rich culture and history of the city. Along the way, we indulged in delicious tapas at local eateries, sipped sangria under the Spanish sun, and danced to lively flamenco music in the streets.\r\n\r\nThe journey was filled with laughter, adventure, and endless exploration. Despite the occasional crowded bus or unexpected detour, we embraced each moment with enthusiasm and curiosity. By the end of the day, we were exhausted but exhilarated, having created lasting memories and forged deeper bonds with each other.\r\n\r\nOverall, the journey was a perfect blend of excitement and relaxation, offering a unique perspective of Barcelona through the lens of public transport. It reminded me of the joy of discovery and the thrill of exploring new places with great company, making it a truly enjoyable experience that I will cherish forever.', '2024-06-29 16:04:17.210759', 'https://study4.com/media/examprep/Post/files/2024/06/26/ielts_speaking_p2_sample_12.png', 'cách học tiếng anh'),
	(4, 'eqweqeewqe', '2024-06-29 16:17:13.595844', 'https://study4.com/media/examprep/Post/files/2024/06/26/ielts_speaking_p2_sample_12.png', 'ưeqweqe'),
