	(1738, 'question38.mp3', 'C', NULL, 38, 'A', 'B', 'C', 'D', NULL, 4, NULL, 'M-Cn: Hi. This is Abdi calling from the Springtown Hotel reservation desk. We received your e-mail regarding your upcoming reservation. (74)\'(75)l see that you asked to move to a room facing the ocean. (75) We make every effort to accommodate such requests, but those rooms are always booked far in advance. Your current room, though, has a lovely view of our garden, which we think you will quite enjoy this time of year. (76) And don\'t forget to bring your swimming suit! Our new pool will be open for the first time this weekend.', 18),
