	(2035, 'question35.mp3', 'C', NULL, 35, 'A', 'B', 'C', 'D', NULL, 4, NULL, 'W-Am: Attention all film lovers! (71) The Braddon Cinema has just opened. Its interior is designed to resemble the classic cinemas from the 1920s. It offers comfortable, reclining seats and individual tray tables for food and drinks. (72) The grand opening is next week and will feature showings of classic films from different eras! (73) And here\'s good advice: to avoid traffic in the city center, the Braddon Cinema is easily reached by riding the train to Center Station.', 21),
